"" tabindex="-1" href="/series/G3KHEVDJ7/the-apothecary-diaries" class="browse-card-hover__title-link--A6aAw" aria-hidden="true">The Apothecary Diaries</a></h3><div class="browse-card-hover__rating-wrapper---39eT"><div class="browse-card-hover__rating-count--ep-6L"><div class="star-rating-short-static--qkdpc star-rating-short-static--is-small--WAjB2" data-t="rating-section"><p class="text--gq6o- text--is-regular--M4487 text--is-m--pqiL- star-rating-short-static__rating--bdAfR">4.9</p><svg class="star-rating-short-static__star-icon--JLlR- base-svg--is-flip--QvCQC" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" data-t="star-svg" aria-hidden="false" role="img" aria-labelledby="star-svg-f47c3e89-6de6-4f46-ae32-d44c60614007"><title id="star-svg-f47c3e89-6de6-4f46-ae32-d44c60614007">Star Review</title><path d="M15.266 8.352L11.988 1.723 8.73 8.352 1.431 9.397 6.71 14.528 5.465 21.849 11.999 18.39 18.544 21.85 17.285 14.528 22.57 9.398z"></path></svg><p class="text--gq6o- text--is-regular--M4487 text--is-m--pqiL- star-rating-short-static__votes-count--h9Sun" data-t="rating-count">(348.1k)</p></div></div></div><div class="browse-card-hover__meta--aB4TP" data-t="meta-info"><div class="browse-card-hover__series-meta--hgyIc"><span class="text--gq6o- text--is-bold--yth2a text--is-m--pqiL-">2 Seasons</span><span class="text--gq6o- text--is-bold--yth2a text--is-m--pqiL-">48 Episodes</span></div></div><p class="text--gq6o- text--is-regular--M4487 text--is-m--pqiL- browse-card-hover__description--e28NH" data-t="description">The Apothecary Diaries is a captivating anime series that weaves together mystery, historical intrigue, and medical science within the richly detailed world of an imperial court. \
\
At the heart of the story is Maomao, a clever young woman obsessed with medicine and poisons. After being kidnapped and sold into servitude in the inner palace, she plans to keep a low profile until she finishes her apprenticeship. However, when she hears of a strange \'93curse\'94 affecting the Imperial Consorts and their children, Maomao reluctantly intervenes, using her expertise to help.\
\
Her efforts attract the attention of Jinshi, a handsome and enigmatic high-ranking eunuch who promotes her to the position of food taster for Imperial Consort Gyokuyou. She soon finds herself entangled in political schemes, hidden dangers, and intricate relationships, all while trying to stay true to her independent nature.\
\
The first season of The Apothecary Diaries centers on Maomao\'92s life as a palace servant, focusing on her curiosity, cleverness, and the daily intricacies of court life. Season 2 shifts toward deeper political intrigue.\
\
The Apothecary Diaries has released two seasons so far, with the first season premiering October 2023 and the second airing January 2025. The series is produced by TOHO Animation STUDIO and OLM, with direction from Norihiro Naganuma for Season 1, and both Naganuma and Akinori Fudesaka for Season 2.</p></div><div class="browse-card-hover__footer--oK4Wg"><div class="browse-card-hover__footer-icon--lJ3B-"><div><div class="tooltip-target--pW1cv"><button aria-label="Play The Apothecary Diaries" tabindex="0" class="tooltip-icon__action-icon-button--KEDNK" data-t="play-button"><svg class="tooltip-icon__action-icon--toIky" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" data-t="play-svg" aria-hidden="false" role="img" aria-labelledby="play-svg-1352dbb3-988a-40e0-9927-95cb39bee6ee"><title id="play-svg-1352dbb3-988a-40e0-9927-95cb39bee6ee">Play</title><path d="M5.944 3C5.385 3 5 3.445 5 4.22v16.018c0 .771.384 1.22.945 1.22.234 0 .499-.078.779-.243l13.553-7.972c.949-.558.952-1.468 0-2.028L6.724 3.243C6.444 3.078 6.178 3 5.944 3m1.057 2.726l11.054 6.503L7 18.732l.001-13.006"></path></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="browse-card-hover__footer-icon--lJ3B-"><div class="tooltip-target--pW1cv"><button aria-label="Add The Apothecary Diaries to watchlist" tabindex="0" class="tooltip-icon__action-icon-button--KEDNK" data-t="add-to-watchlist-btn"><svg class="tooltip-icon__action-icon--toIky" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" data-t="watchlist-svg" aria-hidden="false" role="img" aria-labelledby="watchlist-svg-24050021-4c71-4a02-95b6-f853ab4e005a"><title id="watchlist-svg-24050021-4c71-4a02-95b6-f853ab4e005a">Watchlist</title><path d="M17 18.113l-3.256-2.326A2.989 2.989 0 0 0 12 15.228c-.629 0-1.232.194-1.744.559L7 18.113V4h10v14.113zM18 2H6a1 1 0 0 0-1 1v17.056c0 .209.065.412.187.581a.994.994 0 0 0 1.394.233l4.838-3.455a1 1 0 0 1 1.162 0l4.838 3.455A1 1 0 0 0 19 20.056V3a1 1 0 0 0-1-1z"></path></svg></button></div></div><div class="browse-card-hover_