cription--e28NH" data-t="description">Based off of the original Weekly Shonen Jump manga series from Haruichi Furudate, Haikyu!! is a slice-of-life sports anime revolving around Shoyo Hinata\'92s love of volleyball. Inspired by a small-statured pro volleyball player, Hinata creates a volleyball team in his last year of middle school. Unfortunately the team is matched up against the "King of the Court" Tobio Kageyama\'92s team in their first tournament and inevitably lose. After the crushing defeat, Hinata vows to surpass Kageyama After entering high school, Hinata joins the volleyball team only to find that Tobio has also joined.</p></div><div class="browse-card-hover__footer--oK4Wg"><div class="browse-card-hover__footer-icon--lJ3B-"><div><div class="tooltip-target--pW1cv"><button aria-label="Play Haikyu!!" tabindex="0" class="tooltip-icon__action-icon-button--KEDNK" data-t="play-button"><svg class="tooltip-icon__action-icon--toIky" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" data-t="play-svg" aria-hidden="false" role="img" aria-labelledby="play-svg-37afc04b-a502-462e-85e3-e63d6bac9de9"><title id="play-svg-37afc04b-a502-462e-85e3-e63d6bac9de9">Play</title><path d="M5.944 3C5.385 3 5 3.445 5 4.22v16.018c0 .771.384 1.22.945 1.22.234 0 .499-.078.779-.243l13.553-7.972c.949-.558.952-1.468 0-2.028L6.724 3.243C6.444 3.078 6.178 3 5.944 3m1.057 2.726l11.054 6.503L7 18.732l.001-13.006"></path></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="browse-card-hover__footer-icon--lJ3B-"><div class="tooltip-target--pW1cv"><button aria-label="Add Haikyu!! to watchlist" tabindex="0" class="tooltip-icon__action-icon-button--KEDNK" data-t="add-to-watchlist-btn"><svg class="tooltip-icon__action-icon--toIky" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" data-t="watchlist-svg" aria-hidden="false" role="img" aria-labelledby="watchlist-svg-30f105a0-0137-45e5-a6cd-e6943f1cdc1a"><title id="watchlist-svg-30f105a0-0137-45e5-a6cd-e6943f1cdc1a">Watchlist</title><path d="M17 18.113l-