\"Dive into infinite anime and watch all your favorite titles\\",\\"unavailable_service.explore.vod.cta\\":\\"Visit Crunchyroll\\",\\"unavailable_service.welcome.title\\":\\"Welcome to Crunchyroll!\\",\\"unavailable_service.welcome.body\\":\\"Some experiences are currently unavailable in your region. While you're here, why don't you explore everything that is available to you!\\",\\"unavailable_service.faq.Q1\\":\\"I\'92m a Crunchyroll subscriber - can I get a refund if some services are not available to me?\\",\\"unavailable_service.faq.A1\\":\\"Refunds for Crunchyroll subscriptions are evaluated on a case-by-case basis. If certain services are unavailable to you and you'd like to request a refund, please contact our \\u003ccustomer-service-link\\u003eCustomer Service team\\u003c/customer-service-link\\u003e. They\'92ll review your request and assist you based on your subscription details and our refund policy.\\",\\"unavailable_service.faq.Q2\\":\\"I am a Crunchyroll subscriber and currently visiting Japan, but I can't watch any content.\\",\\"unavailable_service.faq.A2\\":\\"Crunchyroll is only available in certain regions, and unfortunately, it's not available in Japan. We're sorry for the inconvenience.\\",\\"unavailable_service.faq.Q3\\":\\"Where is Crunchyroll Manga available?\\",\\"unavailable_service.faq.A3\\":\\"Crunchyroll Manga is currently available in select countries only. Availability may vary depending on licensing agreements and regional restrictions.\\",\\"unavailable_service.seo.page_title\\":\\"Welcome | Some Experiences Not Available in Your Area | Crunchyroll\\",\\"unavailable_service.seo.page_description\\":\\"Some experiences are not available in your area. While you\'92re here, check out the Anime Awards, our annual celebration of the best of anime. Explore all things anime, including streaming, merchandise, and community events. Are you traveling? Visit our Help Center for more information.\\",\\"seo.region_restricted.page_keywords\\":\\"Crunchyroll, anime, video, streaming, anime shows, streaming service, anime series, anime movies, anime merchandise, anime videos, anime collection, anime awards, awards\\",\\"mark_as_watched.error\\":\\"Something went wrong. Please try again.\\",\\"mark_as_watched.undo\\":\\"Undo\\",\\"series_hero_action_customlist\\":\\"My List\\",\\"series_hero_action_share\\":\\"Share\\",\\"series_hero_action_manga\\":\\"Manga\\",\\"series_hero_action_play_game\\":\\"Play Game\\",\\"series_hero_action_more.tooltip\\":\\"More Options\\",\\"series_hero_action_more.mobile_header\\":\\"More\\",\\"end_slate.recommendations.title\\":\\"Let\'92s find what\'92s next!\\",\\"end_slate.recommendations.details_button\\":\\"Details\\",\\"consent.limited.title\\":\\"We've Updated Our Terms\\",\\"consent.limited.description\\":\\"We've updated our \\u003clink\\u003eTerms of Service\\u003c/link\\u003e for using Crunchyroll. Please review our updated terms. By continuing, you agree to the updated terms.\\",\\"consent.limited.action\\":\\"Continue\\",\\"consent.limited.action_aria\\":\\"I agree to the updated terms and wish to continue to the site\\",\\"consent.error\\":\\"Something went wrong. Please try again.\\",\\"account.password.action\\":\\"Reset password\\",\\"footer.about_crunchyroll.p1\\":\\"Welcome to Crunchyroll, your ultimate destination for streaming anime and the best in anime entertainment. Whether you\'92re a lifelong fan or just starting your anime journey, Crunchyroll offers an extensive library of top-tier anime series and anime movies. From action-packed adventures like Naruto and One Piece to fan-favorites such as Demon Slayer, Solo Leveling, and Attack on Titan, we bring the world of anime right to your screen. With thousands of hours of content, you\'92ll find something for every mood and taste, whether you\'92re into heart-pounding action, touching romance, or gripping mysteries.\\",\\"footer.about_crunchyroll.p2\\":\\"At Crunchyroll, we take pride in being the go-to platform for anime lovers around the world. You can dive into a wide variety of anime genres, including fantasy, slice of life, and sci-fi, ensuring there\'92s always something new to discover.\\",\\"footer.about_crunchyroll.p3\\":\\"With simulcasts straight from Japan, you\'92ll never miss a moment of the latest and greatest new anime releases. Our selection goes beyond just series\'97enjoy a handpicked selection of anime movies that showcase the best in animation and storytelling. Watch anime anytime, anywhere, with the Crunchyroll app available across all your devices.\\",\\"footer.about_crunchyroll.p4\\":\\"Beyond streaming, Crunchyroll is a hub for all things anime. Explore the Crunchyroll Store for exclusive anime merchandise, collectibles, and apparel. Stay updated with Crunchyroll News, delivering the latest on anime, manga, and pop culture. And for gamers, Crunchyroll Games brings your favorite anime worlds to life in exciting and interactive ways. Join the Crunchyroll community and immerse yourself in a world where anime is more than just a genre\'97it\'92s a lifestyle.\\",\\"action.close\\":\\"Close\\",\\"dropdown.filtering\\":\\"Filter\\",\\"dropdown.sorting\\":\\"Sort\\",\\"dropdown.more_options\\":\\"More Options\\",\\"select.seasons\\":\\"Seasons\\",\\"select.simulcast_seasons\\":\\"Simulcast Seasons\\",\\"select.app_language\\":\\"App Language\\",\\"user_menu.label\\":\\"User Menu\\",\\"link.open_in_new_tab\\":\\"\{link\} - open in a new tab\\",\\"captions_styling.select.font\\":\\"Font\\",\\"captions_styling.select.size\\":\\"Size\\",\\"captions_styling.select.color\\":\\"Color\\",\\"captions_styling.select.opacity\\":\\"Opacity\\",\\"captions_styling.select.edge_style\\":\\"Edge Style\\",\\"captions_styling.font_size.large\\":\\"Large\\",\\"captions_styling.font_size.medium\\":\\"Medium\\",\\"captions_styling.font_size.small\\":\\"Small\\",\\"captions_styling.font_color.white\\":\\"White\\",\\"captions_styling.font_color.black\\":\\"Black\\",\\"captions